{"tid":1160900,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分享你最有趣拍拖經歷","createTime":"2019-05-18T18:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T09:33:23.000Z","uid":143093,"like":105,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"80cf59d7125c303143d38471b61daecb68934ea8","tid":1160900,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T18:58:56.000Z","msg":"曾經longd拍拖，同佢一齊好似折磨咁，嗌交一開始係用喊去令我心軟要我氹返佢，之後慢慢用自殺去威脅我唔準分手 仲癲到想逼我返嚟香港讀書陪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當我慢慢習慣咗有佢之後就派帽俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個陣分手佢扮佢阿哥 (佢無阿哥) whatsapp我同我講佢暈咗入院<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但轉個頭俾我見到佢同frd出街 咁我咪篤爆佢 跟住佢話唔信我就要分手<br />\n過咗無耐佢同條仔分手又搵返我，無啦啦話最愛係我，咁我緊係鬧佢：如果當初咁愛我點會派帽俾我？<br />\n佢同我講：我失憶 我個腦有事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老味點解我會同過呢啲人一齊過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：佢有抑鬱 住過院 好似係青山 我宜家諗返起佢啲嘢佢好似有思覺失調"},{"pid":"f2ecb293dc71470e1367c17bc7600fd4c85d534b","tid":1160900,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T19:03:03.000Z","msg":"無人分享？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e3e4ea2951858ff0c2f6d96255c30304555187","tid":1160900,"uid":158899,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T19:18:36.000Z","msg":"連登撚有人拍咩"},{"pid":"3b27cc65455607253d7027a69e06543649926e4d","tid":1160900,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d8e3e4ea2951858ff0c2f6d96255c30304555187","tid":1160900,"uid":158899,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T19:18:36.000Z","msg":"連登撚有人拍咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T19:21:53.000Z","msg":"你又啱 問錯地方"},{"pid":"5320c97b37803ed42ec9d0a876bbba00d0ee2671","tid":1160900,"uid":77792,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T19:36:10.000Z","msg":"以前考dse 考完有個女仔間我攞電話<br />\n之後一齊溫書 溫溫下就當然變左溫女<br />\n最後一齊左幾個月<br />\n成個過程好突然 最後分手好心痛 <br />\n但依家諗返起都幾開心<br />\n好多謝呢個人"},{"pid":"43fc696211cb9a2b1650cc9b9c368a207eb6a1cb","tid":1160900,"uid":28741,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T19:38:25.000Z","msg":"睇戲買最後果排<br />\n然後係度巢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60af538168678f486b8a7c5424ef668295ea5275","tid":1160900,"uid":66436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T19:44:31.000Z","msg":"有趣係邊"},{"pid":"6f4821aaf163655bd877692d9136fae5c895c816","tid":1160900,"uid":136738,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T22:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e2ed3e3e5586029785588b7a739939ab426315","tid":1160900,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5320c97b37803ed42ec9d0a876bbba00d0ee2671","tid":1160900,"uid":77792,"lik